headline: Should You Buy the S&P 500's Highest-Yielding Dividend Stocks Heading Into 2025?
summary: While they aren't as sexy as high-flying growth stocks, they can be just as effective at making investors money.  The steady income from dividend stocks can also help cushion investors against the inevitable volatility of the stock market.  As we head into 2025, it's never too early to begin thinking about which dividend stocks could make sense for your portfolio, especially those with attractive dividend yields.
